data.name: rzxStopToolStripMenuItem1.ToolTipText
data.value: Stops current session, but you can continue recording at a later time.

data.name: rzxFinaliseToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Ends the recording session. The file cannot be used to continue recording later.

data.name: rzxDiscardToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Ends current session without saving any recorded data.
